value.0: Ryll was discovered around 4,800 BBY and is mined on the planet Ryloth. It is a relatively weak form of spice used to create a number of medicines used throughout the Galaxy. It is also smuggled into the Corporate Sector for illegal sale to the workers. As with any recreational substance, Ryll has the potential to be very addictive and dangerous. It can also be combined with Glitterstim to create an even more toxic variation of spice, Glitteryll.
